unisPOEModuleInputError OBJECT-TYPE
      SYNTAX ModuleAlarmState
      MAX-ACCESS read-only
      STATUS current
      DESCRIPTION
             "The node specifies the alarm state:
                                 Input error.
             The value of this node is one of the following values:
                                 normal (1),
                                 alarm  (2)."
